  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv data-component=\"article-header\" data-alignment=\"\" data-stack-meta=\"false\"\u003e\u003ch2 data-component=\"text\" data-alias=\"article-header__headline\" data-alignment=\"\" data-theme=\"headline-md\" data-transform=\"\" data-truncate=\"\" id=\"\"\u003eNetflix’s Christmas NFL Games Average 24 Million Viewers — Audience Peaks With Beyoncé Halftime Performance\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv data-alias=\"gutenberg-content__content\" data-social=\"true\" data-component=\"gutenberg-content\" data-template=\"article\" data-inner-width=\"content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tvline.com/t/netflix/\" id=\"auto-tag_netflix_1\" data-tag=\"netflix\"\u003eNetflix\u003c/a\u003e‘s inaugural \u003cem\u003eNFL Christmas Gameday\u003c/em\u003e presentation of Chiefs vs. Steelers and Ravens vs. Texans averaged more than 24 million viewers for each gridiron match-up.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eRavens-Texans averaged 24.3 million viewers, while Chiefs-Steelers drew 24.1 million — making them  the most-streamed NFL games in U.S. history, according to Nielsen.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eU.S. viewership for NFL Christmas Gameday peaked with \u003ca href=\"https://tvline.com/news/beyonce-nfl-halftime-show-texans-ravens-christmas-game-netflix-1235378601/\"\u003ethe “Beyoncé Bowl” halftime performance\u003c/a\u003e during the \u003cs\u003efirst\u003c/s\u003e second game, which drew north of 27 million viewers.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eTVLine readers gave \u003ca data-id=\"1235378601\" data-type=\"post\" href=\"https://tvline.com/news/beyonce-nfl-halftime-show-texans-ravens-christmas-game-netflix-1235378601/\"\u003eBey’s performance an average grade of “B-.”\u003c/a\u003e\n\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1240\" height=\"843\" src=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?w=650\" alt=\"Netflix NFL Game Viewers Beyonce\" srcset=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg 1240w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?resize=200,136 200w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?resize=300,204 300w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?resize=768,522 768w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?resize=1024,696 1024w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?resize=147,100 147w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?resize=600,408 600w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?resize=275,187 275w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?resize=1000,680 1000w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?resize=244,166 244w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?resize=1160,789 1160w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?resize=140,95 140w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?resize=59,40 59w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?resize=1200,816 1200w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?resize=247,168 247w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?resize=496,337 496w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Gameday-viewers.jpg?resize=993,675 993w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Netflix-NFL-Christmas-Game