p;resize=600%2C400 600w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-episode-3-player-001-front-man.png?w=300\u0026amp;h=200\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=1200%2C800 1200w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/squid-game-episode-3-player-001-front-man.png?w=300\u0026amp;h=200\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=110%2C74 110w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" data-attachment-id=\"1235392606\" data-wp-size=\"nova_size__threebytwo_small_cropped\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe AMA viewership figures cited above are based on Fast National Live Same Day data from Nielsen, which includes out-of-home viewing, CBS local market viewing, and mobile and web data from Netflix and NFL+ mobile viewing from NFL. Global \u003ca href=\"https://tvline.com/t/ratings/\" id=\"auto-tag_ratings_1\" data-tag=\"ratings\"\u003eratings\u003c/a\u003e and additional U.S. viewership insights will be released on Tuesday, Dec. 31.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe second game of the doubleheader, Ravens-Texans, stands as the most-watched Christmas Day game on record among the Adults 18-34 demo, with 5.1 million U.S. viewers in that range tuning in.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e“Bringing our members this record-breaking day of two NFL games was the best Christmas gift we could have delivered,” said Bela Bajaria, Netflix Chief Content Officer. “We’re thankful for our partnership with the NFL, all of our wonderful on-air talent, and let’s please not forget the electrifying Beyoncé and the brilliant Mariah Carey.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
